-Tour.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vans-Warped-Tour-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vans-Warped-Tour-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vans-Warped-Tour-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vans-Warped-Tour-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vans-Warped-Tour-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/a-day-to-remember-interview-big-ole-album-vol-1-surprise-jeremy-mkinnon-bring-me-the-horizon-knocked-loose-3839045">A Day To Remember</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/silverstein">Silverstein</a> and Motion City Soundtrack are among some of the new names added to the line-up for the Vans Warped Tour 2025.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/a-day-to-remember-interview-big-ole-album-vol-1-surprise-jeremy-mkinnon-bring-me-the-horizon-knocked-loose-3839045">A Day To Remember tell us about the surprise release of &#39;Big Ole Album Vol. 1&#39;: “It&#39;s going to show up at your house in three days”</a></strong></li></ul><p> The iconic punk and rock festival is <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/warped-tour-set-to-return-next-year-for-first-time-since-2019-3803876">back this year for its 30th anniversary</a> , six years <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/warped-tour-is-returning-for-25th-anniversary-run-in-2019-2422780">after the previous edition</a> , and will be coming to three cities over three weekends. Other names that have been announced as performers so far, include the likes of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/3oh3">3OH!3</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bowling-for-soup">Bowling For Soup</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beauty-school-dropout">Beauty School Dropout</a> , 408, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fever-333">Fever 333</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/of-mice-and-men">Of Mice &amp; Men</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne</a> .</p><p> The first weekend of the festival will take place at the RFK Campus in Washington DC on June 14 and 15, before it comes to the Shoreline Waterfront in Long Beach, California, on July 26 and 27. On November 15 and 16, it&#39;ll return again, this time at Camping World Stadium Campus in Orlando, Florida. You can find tickets to all three weekends <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fvans-warped-tour-tickets%2Fartist%2F807329" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> Now, it&#39;s been announced that A Day To Remember will be joining the Long Beach and Orlando stops, while Silverstein will play in Washington and Long Beach. Motion City Soundtrack are also on board to play in Washington.</p><p> Also newly announced are From Ashes to New, Attila, Nothing, Nowhere, Mod Sun, I See Stars, Hidden in Plain View, Magnolia Park and more. Visit <a href="https://www.vanswarpedtour.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the official Warped Tour website</a> for further details. </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGbs_Xfy7oS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 